<item>
            <title>[LU-3942] Test failure on test suite sanityn, subtest test_71</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3942</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Bob Glossman &amp;lt;bob.glossman@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/a3cc673e-1bd5-11e3-ae29-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/a3cc673e-1bd5-11e3-ae29-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is the same subtest that fails for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3219&quot; title=&quot;FIEMAP does not sync data or return cached pages&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3219&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3219&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, but reports a different error.  May be a dup, but it&apos;s different enough that I&apos;m raising it as a fresh error.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_71 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1 cancel RPC occured.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanityn 71&lt;/p&gt;</description>
